author: Source: South Wales Guardian
title: Wayne Rooney England's finest, claims Herrera - South Wales Guardian
text:
Rooney ended his final week as a twenty-something with a fine finish in Manchester United's easy 3-0 win at Everton on Saturday. Rooney's 30th birthday next Saturday will provide pundits and commentators with a chance to assess the United and England captain's career.
 South Wales Guardian.
